<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{ title_display }} — 図解（v1）</title>
  {# Tailwind CDN は Raw HTML / htmlpreview 等でブロックされやすいため、見本に近いスタイルをすべて埋め込み CSS で定義する #}
  <style>
    :root {
      --brand-dark: #0c4a6e;
      --brand-mid: #0369a1;
      --brand-light: #e0f2fe;
      --slate-50: #f8fafc;
      --slate-200: #e2e8f0;
      --slate-500: #64748b;
      --slate-600: #475569;
      --slate-800: #1e293b;
      --amber-50: #fffbeb;
      --amber-200: #fde68a;
      --amber-950: #451a03;
      --sky-100: #e0f2fe;
      --sky-200: #bae6fd;
      --white: #fff;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Hiragino Sans", "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", Meiryo, system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--slate-50);
      color: var(--slate-800);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    a { color: var(--brand-mid); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px; }
    a:hover { color: var(--brand-dark); }

    .page-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-dark) 0%, var(--brand-mid) 45%, #0284c7 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      padding: 2.25rem 1rem 2.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.08);
    }
    .page-header-inner {
      max-width: 56rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 0.5rem;
    }
    .page-header-kicker {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgb(224 242 254 / 0.92);
      margin: 0;
    }
    .page-header h1 {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2.8vw, 1.85rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.25;
      word-break: break-word;
    }
    .page-header-sub {
      margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
      max-width: 42rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgb(224 242 254 / 0.95);
    }

    .page-main {
      max-width: 56rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.25rem 1rem 3rem;
    }

    .disclaimer {
      margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--amber-950);
      background: var(--amber-50);
      border: 1px solid var(--amber-200);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }

    .meta-panel {
      margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--slate-600);
      background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.95);
      border: 1px solid var(--slate-200);
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
    }
    .meta-panel p { margin: 0.2rem 0; }
    .meta-label { font-weight: 600; color: var(--slate-500); margin-right: 0.35rem; }
    .meta-panel code {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
      background: #f1f5f9;
    }

    .section-block { margin-bottom: 2.75rem; }
    .section-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--brand-dark);
    }
    .badge {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-width: 2rem;
      height: 2rem;
      padding: 0 0.35rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white);
      background: var(--brand-mid);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--slate-200);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 1.15rem 1.25rem;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05);
    }
    .card-body {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--slate-800);
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--slate-200);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--slate-500);
    }

    @media print {
      body { background: #fff !important; }
      .card { box-shadow: none !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <p class="page-header-kicker">ミクス発売記事ベース・PMDA添付文書抜粋（自動生成）</p>
      <h1>{{ title_display }}</h1>
      <p class="page-header-sub">効能（4）・薬効薬理（18）・臨床成績（17）・副作用（11）・用法・相互作用（6・7・10）</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-main">
    <p class="disclaimer">{{ disclaimer }}</p>

    <div class="meta-panel">
      <p><span class="meta-label">生成</span>{{ generated_at }} / <span class="meta-label">stable_id</span> <code>{{ stable_id }}</code></p>
      <p><span class="meta-label">ミクス</span><a href="{{ rss_link }}" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ rss_link }}</a></p>
      {% if pmda_url %}
      <p><span class="meta-label">PMDA</span><a href="{{ pmda_url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ pmda_url }}</a></p>
      {% endif %}
      {% if source_pdf_url %}
      <p><span class="meta-label">添付文書 PDF</span><a href="{{ source_pdf_url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ source_pdf_url }}</a></p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="badge">1</span>
        識別・製品情報（添付文書 章4より前）
      </h2>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">{{ section_ident or "（識別領域の自動抽出なし）" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="badge">4</span>
        効能又は効果
      </h2>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">{{ section_4 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="badge">18</span>
        薬効薬理
      </h2>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">{{ section_18 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="badge">17</span>
        臨床成績
      </h2>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">{{ section_17 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="badge">11</span>
        副作用
      </h2>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">{{ section_11 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="badge">6–10</span>
        用法・用量・相互作用（メモ）
      </h2>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">{{ section_6710 or "—" }}</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer-note">
      出典: PMDA 公開の添付文書（抜粋・自動生成）。診療・服薬は医師・薬剤師の指示および最新の添付文書に従ってください。KEGG 等の二次出典は v1 では用いていません。
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
